      "text": "Partly agree. Issue would arise when there will be AGI within 2 years, \"employer\" would \"command\" it to ACT as senior DEV, it would pick all knowledge from web, and thousands of those models would run to perform some task. It would pick knowledge from living devs, already dead devs who left some digital trace, etc. So 80% of developers would become obsolete. And this scenario would highly likely happen.",
