      "text": "ChatGPT is my new fantastic mentoring guru in programming. Here's why:\n\n- it is everytime positive, helpful and encouraging\n- is ready to help 24/7\n- is never tired\n- is never angry, even if I ask the same question 100 times\n- shows me how the correct code should look like without any hesitation\n- has no problem returning back to our previous conversations\n- is never pissed off when I ask the same question another senior developer\n- is never jealous that I learned the stuff much easier than it had to do\n- never complains on social platforms how difficult is it to work with those damned juniors\n\nThe only problem I have is that, although still in polite and thankful way, it keeps rejecting my invitations for a beer.",
